trans-unit.source: Provides minimal design-time support for <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte mínimo de tempo de criação para <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> controlos.

trans-unit.source: The ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner class is identical to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner> class and provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> controls.
trans-unit.target: A classe de ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner é idêntica para os <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner>classe e fornece suporte de momento da conceção para <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>controlos.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner>

trans-unit.source: It appears on the design surface as a plain gray box showing the name of the class and the ID of the specific <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: É apresentada na superfície de desenho como uma caixa cinzenta simples que mostra o nome da classe e o ID da especificada <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>controlo.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: You can change the rendering of a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager> control by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method in the same manner as with any standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Pode alterar a composição de um personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>controlar ao substituir o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>método da mesma forma como com qualquer padrão <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is overridden to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>propriedade seja substituída para devolver sempre `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManagerDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets an empty string (""), which indicates that the visual design environment should revert to default control rendering.
trans-unit.target: Obtém uma cadeia vazia (""), que indica que o ambiente de estrutura visual deve reverter a composição do controlo de predefinida.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Vincula o estruturador para associada <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"> </xref> controlo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ProxyWebPartManager"></xref> control associated with the designer.
Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o estruturador deve utilizar uma cópia temporária em vez de controlo real associado o estruturador para gerar a marcação de momento da concepção.
